{"id": "art-242", "label": "Art. 242", "title": "Art. 242", "slug": "art-242", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 242 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>Regulamentul\nintern cuprinde cel pu&#355;in urm&#259;toarele categorii de dispozi&#355;ii:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)reguli\nprivind protec&#355;ia, igiena &#351;i securitatea în munc&#259; în cadrul\nunit&#259;&#355;ii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)reguli\nprivind respectarea principiului nediscrimin&#259;rii &#351;i al\nînl&#259;tur&#259;rii oric&#259;rei forme de înc&#259;lcare a\ndemnit&#259;&#355;ii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)drepturile\n&#351;i obliga&#355;iile angajatorului &#351;i ale salaria&#355;ilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_637508081\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1146\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_637508081\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)procedura de solu&#355;ionare pe cale amiabil&#259; a\nconflictelor individuale de munc&#259;, a cererilor sau a reclama&#355;iilor\nindividuale ale salaria&#355;ilor;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>e)reguli\nconcrete privind disciplina muncii în unitate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>f)abaterile\ndisciplinare &#351;i sanc&#355;iunile aplicabile;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>g)reguli\nreferitoare la procedura disciplinar&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>h)modalit&#259;&#355;ile\nde aplicare a altor dispozi&#355;ii legale sau contractuale specifice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>i)criteriile\n&#351;i procedurile de evaluare profesional&#259; a salaria&#355;ilor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1521354652\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1145\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1521354652\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>j)reguli referitoare la preaviz;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1632834616\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1144\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1632834616\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>k)informa&#355;ii cu privire la politica general&#259; de\nformare a salaria&#355;ilor, dac&#259; exist&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}